      <title>尼日尔撤销许可证后，加拿大铀矿公司股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/canadian-uranium-miner-s-shares-slump-after-niger-revokes-permit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在尼日尔采矿的加拿大公司 GoviEx Uranium Inc. 报道称该西非国家军事领导人撤销了其采矿许可证，随后该公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/canadian-uranium-miner-s-shares-slump-after-niger-revokes-permit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:21:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲银行面临压力测试能力调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/european-banks-face-probe-into-their-stress-testing-abilities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲的银行正面临调查，以检查它们在多大程度上执行了压力测试，而压力测试已成为全球金融危机后银行政策的标志。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/european-banks-face-probe-into-their-stress-testing-abilities</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:04:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲天然气价格波动性较低，表明交易员应避免大举押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/low-volatility-in-european-gas-signals-traders-avoiding-big-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年欧洲天然气期权的波动性有所下降，表明在最近的供应中断凸显该地区天然气供应的脆弱性后，交易商正在避免进行大额押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/low-volatility-in-european-gas-signals-traders-avoiding-big-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:01:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞驳斥民意调查称极右翼未能在法国占据多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-rejects-polls-showing-far-right-short-of-french-majority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞否认了有关她所在的极右翼国民联盟党在法国立法选举中无法获得绝对多数的预测，并警告说，如果她得不到执政授权，她将陷入“泥潭”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-rejects-polls-showing-far-right-short-of-french-majority</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市暴跌之际，中国“国家队”积极投资 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/china-s-national-team-gets-active-in-etfs-as-stocks-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国股市跌破关键心理关口后，一些受到中国主权财富基金青睐的交易所交易基金 (ETF) 的资金流入出现激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/china-s-national-team-gets-active-in-etfs-as-stocks-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称中国人民银行对债券市场的打击将收效甚微</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-salvo-on-bond-rally-may-have-limited-impact-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管央行准备出售数千亿元人民币的债券以冷却股市上涨，但中国观察人士对央行影响收益率下行压力的能力仍表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-salvo-on-bond-rally-may-have-limited-impact-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据公布前全球股市创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在关键的美国就业数据公布之前，全球股市创下历史新高，预计就业数据将显示出就业人数有所放缓。随着工党在英国大选中获胜，英镑创下了四年来最长的连胜纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:19:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦总统称，2030 年前津巴布韦可能会采用 ZiG 作为唯一货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/zimbabwe-president-hints-at-sole-use-of-zig-before-2030-usd-zwg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦暗示，在 2030 年结束现行多货币体系的最后期限之前，该国新的以金银为支撑的货币将成为唯一的法定货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/zimbabwe-president-hints-at-sole-use-of-zig-before-2030-usd-zwg</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度航空公司炸弹威胁不断升级 航班陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/surging-hoax-bomb-threats-on-indian-airlines-cause-flight-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[22 岁的莫利纳·辛格 (Molina Singh) 飞往孟买的航班在途中突然降落，她没有想到自己要在艾哈迈达巴德的小机场等待 12 个小时，还要接受法医笔迹鉴定，行李还会在停机坪上融化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/surging-hoax-bomb-threats-on-indian-airlines-cause-flight-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
